The entirety of the examination will be put under the aegis of the Pushkin Institute for the Russian language, the Russian University of peoples friendship, the Moscow State University, St. Petersburg State University and other Russian universities.
The migrants can pass the tests in all cities; now more than 160 such centers have been opened in Russia already.
The initiative for the introduction of the tests was supported by the members of the State Duma and the Federal Migration Authority.
